sources.description:
Red Prophecies - An American journalist works in Moscow and finds himself embroiled in dangerous political games, the purpose of which is to destabilize the situation in Russia and then interfere with the holdings of the Presidential elections in the United Stares. The journalist begins his own investigation in order to uncover who is behind the operation “Red Prophecies” - special services, financial tycoons or international terrorists?
2014.  Stars: Michael Madsen, Alexander Nevsky, Eric Roberts
